settings.heading: WHY WOULD I WANT YOU TO OPEN IT LIVE INSTEAD OF ME OPENING iT AT HOME?
settings.row_content: Share the fun and excitement of your reveal with your friends, family, and the whole DezLin community! Laugh alongside us with your very own video which is typically created by the owners of DezLin. Ask questions while live if you are there. Your video will be posted on DezLin’s official TikTok account to all of our followers! We will keep your video up indefinitely so you’ll have it to watch, rewatch, share, save, and remember your experience forever.
